MaildirStore personal-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path "~/mail/personal/"
Inbox "~/mail/personal/inbox"
Trash "trash"

IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
Port 993
User "cyphar@cyphar.com"
PassCmd +"keepassxc-helper '/Shared/Email/Mailbox'"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Account mailbox

Channel personal-inbox
Master :mailbox-remote:
Slave :personal-local:
Sync All
Expunge Both
Create Both
CopyArrivalDate yes

Channel personal-sent
Master :mailbox-remote:Sent
Slave :personal-local:sent
Sync All
Expunge Both
Create Both
CopyArrivalDate yes

Channel personal-archives
Master :mailbox-remote:
Slave :personal-local:
Pattern Archives/*
Sync All
Expunge Both
Create Both
CopyArrivalDate yes

Group personal
Channels personal-inbox personal-sent
